----- stdout -----
Manage plugins (requires Milestone 6)

Usage: borrow-checker plugin [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>

Commands:
  install  Install a plugin from a `.wasm` file or the plugin registry
  list     List installed plugins
  remove   Remove an installed plugin by name
  help     Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
      --json
          Emit machine-readable JSON instead of human-readable output
          
          [env: BC_JSON=]

      --db-path <DB_PATH>
          Path to the SQLite database file
          
          [env: BC_DB_PATH=[TEMP_DIR]/test.db]

  -v, --verbose...
          Increase log verbosity.
          
          Pass once for info (`-v`), twice for debug (`-vv`), three times for trace (`-vvv`). Use `RUST_LOG` for fine-grained per-crate control.

  -q, --quiet...
          Decrease log verbosity.
          
          Pass once for error-only output (`-q`). Use `RUST_LOG` for fine-grained per-crate control.

  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')
